title: Intense Robot
description:
Two scientists get to know the robot they've created.

Written by Ariel Karlin
Featuring Willy Appelman, Maya Deshmukh and Tristan Griffin
Directed by Matt Gehring
Shot by Thursday Shoots
Edited by Phillip Russell
